Most times patients may forget to take the medicines at proper time as per the specified in the prescription which may cause late recovery from the disease/illness. So it is necessary to take proper medicines in the proper quantity at the proper time. This project is about pill reminder application for the patients. It requires less time and a little effort.

The main objective of this project is to implement the algorithm in python using Tesseract and recognize the medicines and timing they are supposed to be taken.This application will remind their user to take proper medicines in proper quantity at proper time by automatically setting the reminders. These reminders will be automatically set by the application as per the prescription. This reminder will remind the user patient that now itâ€™s time to take the medicine.

Optical character recognition or optical character reader is the electronic or mechanical conversion of images of typed, handwritten or printed text into machine-encoded text, whether from a scanned document, a photo of a document, a scene-photo or from subtitle text superimposed on an image. With the advent of technology, character recognition  has gained a lot of importance especially in fields like banking,where OCR is used to process checks without human involvement.
 
